    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so there\u2019s not a speck of wear to be found. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for its next adventure. I'm so excited for whoever gets to take this home!",
