    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Carbon Black Metallic. This example features the S54 3.2L atmospheric straight-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. Mechanically superlative, the vehicle has undergone documented preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul. The Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission shifts with clinical precision, paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The rear subframe has been structurally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity. The exterior retains its factory depth with no signs of orange peel or oxidation, while the undercarriage is devoid of any galvanic corrosion. This is a turn-key, concours-level specimen for the serious enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
