    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b You won't believe how gorgeous this ride is! I\u2019ve taken absolute pride in keeping this car in tip-top shape, and honestly, it looks and feels practically brand new\u2014seriously, it\u2019s flawless inside and out. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, and I\u2019m looking for someone who will love it just as much as I have. Come take it for a spin, I promise you'll fall in love the moment you sit inside! \u2728",
